---
// knomit is a dark-only product. Pin the dark palette and ignore the OS
// preference + any stored choice, so /docs never flashes or settles into light.
// Inlined to run before paint (avoids FOUC). Replaces Starlight's provider.
---

<script is:inline>
  document.documentElement.dataset.theme = 'dark';
  // ThemeSelect is removed, but other Starlight scripts call into this global.
  window.StarlightThemeProvider = { updatePickers() {} };
</script>
